name: Earthbound Geoglyph
desc: While a Level 10 monster is on the field, neither player can target this card with card effects, also it cannot be destroyed by card effects. Synchro Monsters can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of your "Earthbound Immortal" monster. If a Synchro Monster(s) is Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Earthbound Immortal" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand. You can only use this effect of "Earthbound Geoglyph" once per turn.
